2
00:02:17.080 --> 00:02:21.919
We have no time to waste
with words or councils.

3
00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:28.319
I assigned Sahinshah Bey as
the commander of my army...

4
00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:35.959
to conquer Bursa
as soon as possible.

5
00:02:48.200 --> 00:02:51.279
-How so?
-From now on.

6
00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:58.959
Alaeddin Bey is in charge
of leading the whole beylic.

7
00:03:04.880 --> 00:03:12.239
He will be my shadow on
our land within our borders.

8
00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:43.079
Dumrul. Balaban.

9
00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:49.839
Take alps with you and burn down all
the ports. lighthouses and beaches around.

10
00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:54.559
Neither food nor a single grain of
wheat. neither a soldier nor an army...

11
00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:57.679
will come to Bursa
from Constantinople.

12
00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:59.639
-Go!
-As you order. my Bey.

13
00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.999
-As you order. my Bey!
-Let's go!

14
00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:07.239
We'll be late for
the council. brother.

15
00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:10.319
I said we'd prefer hunting
rather than a council.

16
00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:13.879
The hunt turned out to be
more fruitful than the council.

17
00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:16.439
Let's get to the tribe quickly.

18
00:04:16.640 --> 00:04:20.799
We will give Osman Bey the great
news and capture Bursa next.

19
00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:24.639
-Let's go. Come on.
-Come on!

20
00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:32.999
Obviously. she can
feel the coming storm.

21
00:04:33.320 --> 00:04:36.079
See? She doesn't
know what to do.

22
00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:39.839
Well... Her husband
lost the battle.

23
00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:43.039
And he didn't join the council.

24
00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:46.319
This is not good at all.

25
00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:18.079
Congratulations. Alaeddin.

26
00:05:18.280 --> 00:05:20.559
Thank you. my Bey.

27
00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:33.359
=Mother.
-What is it. mother?

28
00:05:33.880 --> 00:05:35.879
Gonca Hatun.

29
00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:43.839
Osman Bey gave Alaeddin Bey all the rule of the
beylic. Sogut. Inegol and all the other lands.

30
00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:49.479
Thanks to Allah.

31
00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:53.559
Finally. Alaeddin
got what he deserves.

32
00:05:54.760 --> 00:05:59.239
When did we not give Alaeddin what he
deserved? Why are you saying that Gonca?

33
00:06:01.200 --> 00:06:03.759
What about Orhan Bey?

34
00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:09.279
Osman Bey dismissed
Orhan Bey from his duty.

35
00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:14.639
My father is in charge
of the siege now.

36
00:06:15.440 --> 00:06:19.079
How could they make such a
decision without Orhan Bey?

37
00:06:23.400 --> 00:06:25.799
Did no Beys support him?

38
00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.999
-Nobody?
-Enough.

39
00:06:28.480 --> 00:06:31.679
The final word hasn't
been spoken yet.

40
00:06:38.320 --> 00:06:42.079
It seems mother has forgotten
who says th final word.

41
00:06:43.200 --> 00:06:48.639
She feels sorry for a son but she can't even think
about being happy for her another son Alaeddin.

42
00:06:51.760 --> 00:06:56.239
Do you think Malhun discriminates
between her sons. Gonca?

43
00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:02.199
Alaeddin deserved
this title years ago.

44
00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:05.079
But we kept silent. Nilufer.

45
00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:10.319
See? You be ame a fireball in case of
the first decision against your husband.

46
00:07:11.320 --> 00:07:13.839
Alaeddin already
deserved this title.

47
00:07:14.360 --> 00:07:17.679
And he got his title
fairly like he deserved.

48
00:07:17.920 --> 00:07:19.159
Thanks to Allah.

49
00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:21.999
What about Orhan Bey?

50
00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:29.119
Is it appropriate that all th efforts and
achievements of Orhan Bey are being ignored?

51
00:07:29.760 --> 00:07:34.799
Did Orhan Bey get victorious
on his own. Nilufer Hatun?

52
00:07:35.320 --> 00:07:38.079
Didn't all the beys help him?

53
00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:43.159
Didn't Sahinshah Bey fight beside
him and dodge the death many times?

54
00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:45.559
I appreciate that.

55
00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:48.079
The council's
decision makes it clear.

56
00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:52.559
They showed how much they
supported him in the first defeat.

57
00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:11.799
Sahinshah Bey. go to the
headquarters immediately.

58
00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:15.359
Keep alps and beys in order.

59
00:08:15.880 --> 00:08:21.959
It an honor for me to carry out
the duty you gave me. Osman Bey.

60
00:08:22.120 --> 00:08:24.639
Thank you.

61
00:08:25.360 --> 00:08:28.799
May Allah help
you be victorious.

62
00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:45.039
Does anyone have
something to say ..

63
00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:48.719
Before the council is over?

64
00:09:04.280 --> 00:09:07.199
Do I have permission. Osman Bey?

65
00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:13.439
May my words be
heard as the

66
00:09:13.440 --> 00:09:20.359
words of Mother Haime who once ruled
in this chair and led many Kayi commanders.

67
00:09:22.160 --> 00:09:27.839
Council is the place of ounseling. It ends
only when the words to say are finished.

68
00:09:28.560 --> 00:09:30.799
I have words to say.

69
00:09:31.040 --> 00:09:36.639
You have a place in the council
and power in the tribe. Malhun Hatun.

70
00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:39.439
Go ahead.

71
00:09:47.640 --> 00:09:54.039
My words are for Orhan Bey
who got dismissed from his duty.

72
00:09:57.480 --> 00:09:59.519
Mother.

73
00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:01.319
What are you doing?

74
00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:07.079
Your tongu may keep silent about your brother
But don't expect me to do the same. Alaeddin Bey.

75
00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:14.039
-Mother.
-Alaeddin.

76
00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:26.399
It seems Malhun Hatun isn't
pleased with what she has heard.

77
00:10:30.360 --> 00:10:33.039
It's not about
what I have heard.

78
00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:37.999
It's about what Orhan
hasn't heard yet.

79
00:10:38.920 --> 00:10:45.239
Not a single word has been said about the fact
that his duty he devoted his life and years to...

80
00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:48.039
has been taken away from him.

81
00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:54.599
It was my order Malhun Hatun.

82
00:10:54.920 --> 00:10:57.039
Your order is my
command my Bey.

83
00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:58.599
When the council is over.

84
00:10:58.800 --> 00:11:03.239
Neither the ouncil nor
the words are over yet.

85
00:11:03.400 --> 00:11:09.399
Didn't even a single one of yours
defend Orhan Bey in this council??

86
00:11:11.880 --> 00:11:14.319
I'm asking you. Beys.

87
00:11:16.040 --> 00:11:18.079
His brother has got mute.

88
00:11:18.280 --> 00:11:24.399
Even his right hand Sahinshah Bey got
frustrated with the defeat in the last battle.

89
00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:29.959
What about you?

90
00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:32.879
Is this how you
show your fellowship?

91
00:11:33.280 --> 00:11:39.439
Couldn't one of you think that the Bey's
decision should be said to Orhan Bey's face?

92
00:11:41.080 --> 00:11:44.159
Why didn't you mention that?

93
00:11:45.120 --> 00:11:51.599
Was it this hard to defend Orhan
Bey who you fought with for years?

94
00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:55.679
Show us. hatun. Where is he?

95
00:11:56.040 --> 00:11:59.079
So I can say it to his face too.

96
00:11:59.400 --> 00:12:03.159
Where is Orhan Bey hatun?

97
00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:08.239
Shouldn't you ask this to
him when he is back. my Bey?

98
00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:40.719
Both the council
and words are over.

99
00:12:41.080 --> 00:12:45.039
Get the council feast prepared
for the Beys immediately.

100
00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:50.999
Aykurt. bring doctor to me.

101
00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:53.599
As you order my Bey.

102
00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:13.319
You have a voice in the
council. Malhun Hatun.

103
00:13:13.760 --> 00:13:19.199
But your words should have
been the voice of the state.

104
00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:23.879
Not a mother's voice
who felt sorry for her son.

105
00:13:24.440 --> 00:13:27.559
Your grief about one son...

106
00:13:27.800 --> 00:13:32.159
shouldn't cast a shad w over
your happiness about your other son.

107
00:13:35.280 --> 00:13:40.639
Sahinshah Bey. my son
Alaeddin got what he deserved.

108
00:13:41.440 --> 00:13:44.399
As to your duty.

109
00:13:44.680 --> 00:13:47.559
Orhan Bey isn't dead vet.

110
00:13:49.720 --> 00:13:52.999
Congratulations about
your new title. Alaeddin Bey.

111
00:13:53.320 --> 00:13:57.839
I have no doubts that you
will be worthy of your title.

112
00:13:58.600 --> 00:14:02.679
I wish you had a heart
to defend your brother.

113
00:14:16.440 --> 00:14:22.119
I'll get a glorious funeral for
Octavius like he deserved.

114
00:14:22.200 --> 00:14:25.319
At least as splendid
as your father's.

115
00:14:25.560 --> 00:14:29.439
As long as Orhan and Osman don't
swing on a rope on the city walls of Bursa.

116
00:14:29.640 --> 00:14:31.439
no ceremonies will matter.

117
00:14:31.600 --> 00:14:34.319
You're right. We are
deeply grieved.

118
00:14:34.600 --> 00:14:42.119
However. Bursa is safe as long as
they don't find out where the tunnel is.

119
00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:55.319
Orhan wouldn't leave
his victory unfinished.

120
00:14:58.360 --> 00:15:01.679
You three. come with me.

121
00:15:05.120 --> 00:15:07.759
Dog feels disturbed.

122
00:15:08.200 --> 00:15:10.959
It means there is
something here.

123
00:15:32.840 --> 00:15:35.639
Finally! We found
the tunnel entrance.

124
00:15:35.800 --> 00:15:38.639
We hould inform
our Bey quickly.

125
00:15:40.680 --> 00:15:43.759
You came a long way.
You can't leave so fast.

126
00:15:44.080 --> 00:15:47.039
Surround them

127
00:15:48.560 --> 00:15:51.319
Are there any other men around?

128
00:15:52.640 --> 00:15:55.559
Are there any other
men around? Speak!

129
00:16:08.800 --> 00:16:11.319
Search the field!
Leave nobody alive!

130
00:16:11.600 --> 00:16:14.039
Leave nobody alive!

131
00:16:14.680 --> 00:16:17.679
You did a good job.

132
00:16:19.320 --> 00:16:21.839
Unfinished job as long
as Orhan isn't among them.

133
00:16:22.040 --> 00:16:26.079
The soldiers watching our back on the
way were under your command right?

134
00:16:26.480 --> 00:16:30.119
My apologies. sir

135
00:16:31.800 --> 00:16:32.959
Look at me!

136
00:16:33.080 --> 00:16:37.199
From now on. you all
have to be more careful!

137
00:16:37.360 --> 00:16:41.919
The tunnel is the
last chance for Bursa!

138
00:16:42.120 --> 00:16:46.159
Let's go talk to Boran and ask
him if he got inside through here.

139
00:16:46.440 --> 00:16:50.719
Remove these bodies! If
Orhan's men see the bodies.

140
00:16:50.960 --> 00:16:54.039
they will know the
tunnel is here! Come on!

141
00:17:04.440 --> 00:17:07.839
Sahin hah Bey.
congratulations about your duty.

142
00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:10.199
-Alaaddin Bey ongratulations.
-EyvAllah.

143
00:17:10.200 --> 00:17:11.999
-Congratulations. my Bey.
-EyvAllah.

144
00:17:12.240 --> 00:17:14.959
EyvAllah. Thank you.

145
00:17:23.160 --> 00:17:25.839
Turahan Bey. Temurboga.

146
00:17:26.000 --> 00:17:28.399
You look disturbed
since the council.

147
00:17:28.520 --> 00:17:30.999
Is it appropriate for
Beys to look like that?

148
00:17:31.040 --> 00:17:34.279
When Malhun Hatun showed
up. I got ashamed of myself.

149
00:17:34.680 --> 00:17:36.559
That's why. Sahinshah Bey.

150
00:17:36.840 --> 00:17:42.119
My mother defended my brother's right. And my
father did what the justice requires. Turahan.

151
00:17:43.200 --> 00:17:45.279
That's it.

152
00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:51.879
InshaAllah. Sahinshah Bey
won't let us down. Alaeddin Bey.

153
00:17:54.160 --> 00:17:57.639
Did I ever let you
down. Temurboga?

154
00:17:57.920 --> 00:18:00.759
Trying to cause unrest
when we should stand united?

155
00:18:01.400 --> 00:18:05.119
Don't you talk to me about
causing unrest. Sahinshah!

156
00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:08.359
If you have words to say. you
should have said them inside!

157
00:18:08.560 --> 00:18:09.919
This is causing unrest!

158
00:18:10.040 --> 00:18:12.119
Watch your words. Sahinshah.

159
00:18:12.240 --> 00:18:13.519
Enough!

160
00:18:13.640 --> 00:18:16.119
If you appear b fore
me with such noise again.

161
00:18:16.280 --> 00:18:19.639
I will punish you all!

162
00:18:37.960 --> 00:18:39.919
Sari Halil!

163
00:18:40.200 --> 00:18:43.799
Halime. did my facc get wound d
in the battle and you didn't tell me?

164
00:18:43.960 --> 00:18:45.439
People don't recognize me

165
00:18:45.560 --> 00:18:48.639
They ignore and stay
away from you. my Bey.

166
00:18:48.880 --> 00:18:53.599
Someone put the blame of Bursa defeat
on you. People may be upset about that.

167
00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:55.959
Both victory and
defeat are from Allah.

168
00:18:56.080 --> 00:18:59.519
They seem
embarrassed. not upset.

169
00:19:01.120 --> 00:19:04.559
That's weird.
We'll find out soon.

170
00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:21.119
Brother.

171
00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:35.159
Welcome my Bey.

172
00:19:37.400 --> 00:19:41.559
Everyones es m but only
you welcomed me. Cerkutay Bey.

173
00:19:42.960 --> 00:19:47.079
Welcome. brother.
Thank you. brother. What is the matter?

174
00:19:47.600 --> 00:19:51.639
Since I came back. everyone has
run away from me as if I were a leper.

175
00:19:52.560 --> 00:19:54.719
Where have you been. brother?

176
00:19:54.960 --> 00:19:59.039
How could you disappear right
before the council without informing?

177
00:20:05.640 --> 00:20:08.519
I can see the feast. which
means the council is over.

178
00:20:08.760 --> 00:20:11.999
Let me fill my stomach first.

179
00:20:13.040 --> 00:20:18.639
Brother. I asked where you have been.
What's the haste. brother? Calm down.

180
00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:24.399
Osman Bey made important
decisions in the council.

181
00:20:25.520 --> 00:20:29.119
Considering he did that without
me. they must be very important.

182
00:20:33.600 --> 00:20:36.279
Osman Bey...

183
00:20:37.640 --> 00:20:41.759
assigned Alaaddin
Bey as his regent.

184
00:20:54.240 --> 00:20:56.199
Congratulations brother.

185
00:20:56.480 --> 00:20:59.799
Congratulations
about being the regent.

186
00:21:02.720 --> 00:21:07.119
I'm sorry just because we can't be
together in the army camp any longer.

187
00:21:09.040 --> 00:21:11.439
You.

188
00:21:12.160 --> 00:21:15.119
Won't be inth army
camp anymore. brother.

189
00:21:19.880 --> 00:21:24.119
And you think you can know where
the alps should stand. Alaeddin?

190
00:21:24.960 --> 00:21:28.439
Oh. brother...

191
00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:36.119
Osman Bey dismissed you
from commanding. brother.

192
00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:40.999
What? What are
you saying. brother?

193
00:21:41.160 --> 00:21:47.479
And he assigned Sahinshah
Bey as the commander instead.

194
00:21:48.280 --> 00:21:52.839
Now tell me. Where did you
go before the council. brother?

195
00:21:53.280 --> 00:21:56.479
Brother. tell him.

196
00:21:58.000 --> 00:22:01.599
I was going after
the enemy. Alaeddin.

197
00:22:01.960 --> 00:22:06.119
I thought my brother would
defend me in the council.

198
00:22:09.880 --> 00:22:12.919
What did you do. Alaeddin?

199
00:22:13.080 --> 00:22:16.999
What did you say while my father
sacrificed me in the council. Alaeddin?

200
00:22:17.000 --> 00:22:19.639
Nobody can talk against
father's words. brother.

201
00:22:19.840 --> 00:22:21.239
You know that.

202
00:22:21.480 --> 00:22:24.279
Except Malhun Hatun.

203
00:22:26.080 --> 00:22:29.119
She is a mother after all.

204
00:22:31.120 --> 00:22:35.639
It seems my mother spoke with the heart
of a mother and the mind of the state.

205
00:22:36.720 --> 00:22:39.519
And you Beys?

206
00:22:40.360 --> 00:22:42.319
You;

207
00:22:42.720 --> 00:22:45.999
How could you keep silent?

208
00:22:47.120 --> 00:22:49.159
You should have informed me...

209
00:22:49.400 --> 00:22:51.479
and attended
the council. brother.

210
00:22:51.600 --> 00:22:54.839
Keeping silent means
showing your side. brother.

211
00:22:55.480 --> 00:22:57.119
You showed your side.

212
00:22:57.280 --> 00:22:59.759
This is not a good
place. my Beys.

213
00:22:59.960 --> 00:23:02.199
You're right. Cerkutay Bey.

214
00:23:02.720 --> 00:23:05.039
This is not a good place.

215
00:23:05.560 --> 00:23:07.799
-Are you mad. brother?
-Get out of my way.

216
00:23:07.920 --> 00:23:11.079
-Brother!
-Get out of my way!

217
00:23:24.600 --> 00:23:28.319
Don't let your anger swallow
your brother Alaeddin Bey.

218
00:23:28.320 --> 00:23:30.559
Right.

219
00:23:35.120 --> 00:23:38.719
My feet are taking
revenge of years from me.

220
00:23:38.840 --> 00:23:41.359
What revenge are
you taking. doctor?

221
00:23:41.520 --> 00:23:43.839
Rub it slowly.

222
00:24:24.240 --> 00:24:26.599
What is it?

223
00:24:27.320 --> 00:24:30.559
Are you here to
sew with sword...

224
00:24:31.040 --> 00:24:34.039
what was cut with an order?

225
00:24:37.120 --> 00:24:43.999
I'm not talking to you as your son Orhan but
Orhan Bey who was your commander for years.

226
00:24:44.560 --> 00:24:48.319
What's the reason
why you did this to me?

227
00:24:51.640 --> 00:24:55.879
You couldn't capture
Bursa. I kept silent.

228
00:24:56.120 --> 00:25:00.799
I though Orhan must
hav an explanation.

229
00:25:01.200 --> 00:25:06.119
But there is no explanation for
not attending the council. Orhan.

230
00:25:06.320 --> 00:25:09.119
-There is an explanation.
-Quiet.

231
00:25:11.160 --> 00:25:14.519
You should have said
your words before you left.

232
00:25:14.960 --> 00:25:16.679
I couldn't. my Bey

233
00:25:16.920 --> 00:25:18.119
You didn't listen to me.

234
00:25:18.160 --> 00:25:20.199
You should have
talked to your brother.

235
00:25:20.240 --> 00:25:21.959
Or your mother.

236
00:25:22.120 --> 00:25:25.439
Or your Beys whose
opinions you asked for!

237
00:25:25.600 --> 00:25:30.599
And they would have told you that
nothing is more important than the council.

238
00:25:32.960 --> 00:25:38.759
What did you achieve by leaving except
justifying the Beys who says you are bull-headed?

239
00:25:38.880 --> 00:25:41.839
You harmed both yourself and me.

240
00:25:42.040 --> 00:25:44.919
You went to Bursa
in a wrong time.

241
00:25:45.400 --> 00:25:49.079
And I lost Orhan.

242
00:25:50.480 --> 00:25:55.159
You left the council in a wrong
time and lost the command.

243
00:25:56.120 --> 00:26:01.599
From now on.
you are just an alp.

244
00:26:03.840 --> 00:26:05.479
Don't!

245
00:26:05.640 --> 00:26:08.399
Don't take another
step. brother.

246
00:26:19.680 --> 00:26:24.559
The sword you gave me as the present
with the mission of conquest years ago.

247
00:26:28.440 --> 00:26:32.039
You think I'm not worthy.

248
00:26:32.720 --> 00:26:35.119
Take it. my Bey.

249
00:26:41.360 --> 00:26:44.439
I'm ready to accept
whatever comes from Allah...

250
00:26:45.040 --> 00:26:48.399
and to be your sacrifice.

251
00:27:20.240 --> 00:27:23.039
What Alaeddin?

252
00:27:24.720 --> 00:27:27.479
You got concerns
about your brother?

253
00:27:30.640 --> 00:27:33.119
Get out.

254
00:27:42.200 --> 00:27:46.759
I'm ready to accept whatever comes
from Allah and to be your sacrifice.

255
00:27:52.920 --> 00:27:55.879
Brother.

256
00:27:56.720 --> 00:27:59.319
For a moment. I thought...

257
00:27:59.920 --> 00:28:02.399
You thought what?

258
00:28:05.760 --> 00:28:08.839
That I'd take ba k with sword
what was taken with an order?

259
00:28:09.160 --> 00:28:11.439
I know the times
you got mad. brother.

260
00:28:11.560 --> 00:28:13.999
Brother Orhan. Brother Alaeddin.

261
00:28:14.120 --> 00:28:16.839
Stay out of my way.

262
00:28:18.440 --> 00:28:21.759
I will stay out of your way.

263
00:29:24.680 --> 00:29:26.999
Come Halil. come.

264
00:29:33.080 --> 00:29:36.319
That day when we were
cutting off the road in Bursa...

265
00:29:36.640 --> 00:29:41.599
a branch of Kayi s great plane
tree was cut off at the council.

266
00:29:42.040 --> 00:29:44.119
I know my Bey.

267
00:29:44.360 --> 00:29:48.879
I know but.. if that branch is cut off. it
is to make sure it comes back stronger.

268
00:29:48.960 --> 00:29:52.999
You see the men that wander around that
tree with axes in their hands right. Halil?

269
00:29:53.000 --> 00:29:55.159
Yes my Bey.

270
00:29:55.240 --> 00:29:56.959
I do.

271
00:29:57.200 --> 00:30:02.319
I also see the men that are trying to make
that axe look good and make Osman Bey hold it.

272
00:30:02.880 --> 00:30:06.519
Then why doesn't
my father see it Halil?

273
00:30:07.000 --> 00:30:11.479
Where does my brother look while
my father looks at the other way?

274
00:30:11.640 --> 00:30:14.959
What do you see that
I don't see? Tell me.

275
00:30:16.560 --> 00:30:19.559
My Bey. You also know.

276
00:30:19.760 --> 00:30:23.079
Everyone is afraid
of facing disunion.

277
00:30:23.200 --> 00:30:24.919
Sahinshah's Beys...

278
00:30:24.920 --> 00:30:30.039
-after Bursa...
-We will not let them cause that disunion.

279
00:30:30.800 --> 00:30:33.919
We won t let them cut another...

280
00:30:34.120 --> 00:30:38.319
branch or flower off
of that tree anymore.

281
00:30:38.720 --> 00:30:41.839
We won't let the ones
outside or insid ...

282
00:30:42.080 --> 00:30:45.119
do that.

283
00:30:46.800 --> 00:30:49.519
Let them ct like they
are forest guards. my Bey.

284
00:30:50.360 --> 00:30:53.679
We will keep walking on our way.

285
00:30:54.920 --> 00:30:57.839
EyvAllah.

286
00:31:04.440 --> 00:31:06.199
Where are you headed to my Bey;

287
00:31:06.200 --> 00:31:09.559
I will get rid of the dust and soil that
has settled on me in the tribe. Halil.

288
00:31:09.600 --> 00:31:11.759
Keep being my
eyes and ears here.

289
00:31:11.880 --> 00:31:15.159
Always look ahead my Bey. I
will always stand behind you.

290
00:31:15.240 --> 00:31:18.679
EyvAllah.

291
00:31:49.720 --> 00:31:51.599
Tell me.

292
00:31:51.760 --> 00:31:55.719
Did your brother take
you there with him...

293
00:31:56.800 --> 00:32:01.359
or did you set out
on your own after him?

294
00:32:01.480 --> 00:32:02.999
He didn't even know. father.

295
00:32:03.040 --> 00:32:06.279
He was going to bring the good
news about his victory to you.

296
00:32:06.400 --> 00:32:09.239
What victory?

297
00:32:09.440 --> 00:32:12.599
-He didn't tell you right?
-What didn't he tell me. Halime?

298
00:32:12.720 --> 00:32:15.519
He must've remained
silent out of respect. father.

299
00:32:15.560 --> 00:32:18.039
Apparently. he didn't
want to offend his father.

300
00:32:18.080 --> 00:32:20.079
Halime. why would he do that?!

301
00:32:20.120 --> 00:32:24.199
In Gemlik. he defeated the army
that was sent from Constantinople!

302
00:32:24.400 --> 00:32:28.679
He didn t tell you that he found the
harbour that sent Bursa food and weapons!

303
00:32:28.720 --> 00:32:33.399
He didn't tell you that he ruined Bursa's
secret treasure and ammunition. father!

304
00:32:39.440 --> 00:32:40.439
Good.

305
00:32:43.000 --> 00:32:49.439
It would be fitting for him to hand
over the command with such a victory.

306
00:32:49.880 --> 00:32:54.239
He carried out his duty
until the very last moment.

307
00:32:54.280 --> 00:32:57.599
From now on. his duty...

308
00:32:57.680 --> 00:33:01.799
will be serving
me like an Alp.

309
00:33:01.880 --> 00:33:04.119
My brother did not
deserve this. father!

310
00:33:04.160 --> 00:33:09.439
Only I can decide if he
deserves more or less.

311
00:33:11.920 --> 00:33:15.439
Leave now.

312
00:35:12.360 --> 00:35:15.519
My father's dream came true.

313
00:35:15.560 --> 00:35:18.759
The knife he put on my
throat was able to cut.

314
00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:22.679
He sacrificed his son...

315
00:35:22.840 --> 00:35:25.799
and the efforts made for
years with a blind dagger.

316
00:35:47.920 --> 00:35:49.519
Where is your sword?

317
00:35:49.680 --> 00:35:52.399
I gave it back to its owner.

318
00:35:52.480 --> 00:35:55.919
Your father gave it to you so
you could open Bursa's gate with 1it.

319
00:35:56.240 --> 00:35:58.639
My father can hand it
to its n w owner now.

320
00:35:58.720 --> 00:36:01.959
My father dismissed you. But
did that really make you give up?

321
00:36:02.000 --> 00:36:06.799
I am struggling with Beys at my table on
one hand. with my brother on the other hand.

322
00:36:07.000 --> 00:36:09.399
I cannot do it with that sword.

323
00:36:09.440 --> 00:36:14.079
So that this is a new battle.
my sword must be new as well.

324
00:36:15.480 --> 00:36:19.839
-So you won't give up on Bursa.
-Never.

325
00:36:20.640 --> 00:36:24.839
I will take Bursa and the sword
that I gave back to my father.

326
00:36:25.520 --> 00:36:28.079
With my own methods.

327
00:36:28.600 --> 00:36:31.079
Even if I am left alone.

328
00:36:31.280 --> 00:36:34.719
You are not alone.

329
00:36:47.800 --> 00:36:50.559
Do not tell anything to
Kasim and Suleyman.

330
00:36:50.640 --> 00:36:53.039
I entrusted them
to groom Aykurt.

331
00:36:53.280 --> 00:36:55.599
So they wouldn't
hear the others talking.

332
00:36:56.080 --> 00:36:59.639
You did well. They
should hear it from me.

333
00:37:08.840 --> 00:37:12.439
Was this supposed to be the reward
for what my brother did mother?!

334
00:37:12.560 --> 00:37:16.759
My brother has not slept
on a soft bed for years!

335
00:37:18.360 --> 00:37:20.319
What is my father
trying to do. mother?!

336
00:37:20.440 --> 00:37:22.999
Bursa is my brother s
reason to live!

337
00:37:23.040 --> 00:37:26.799
My brother will not give up on
Bursa. Doesn't my father know that?

338
00:37:26.840 --> 00:37:28.799
He won't give up.

339
00:37:28.960 --> 00:37:32.319
My Orhan is
stubborn like his father.

340
00:37:32.800 --> 00:37:36.559
My daughter who carries
embers in her heart... Come here.

341
00:37:38.160 --> 00:37:41.239
Calm down.

342
00:37:42.080 --> 00:37:44.439
What did you say at
the council. mother?

343
00:37:44.480 --> 00:37:45.839
Did you defend my brother?

344
00:37:45.840 --> 00:37:47.999
Did you think I
would remain silent?

345
00:37:48.000 --> 00:37:50.399
I told them what was
the right thing to do.

346
00:37:50.440 --> 00:37:53.879
I also won t remain silent I'll
follow my brother wherever he goes!

347
00:37:53.920 --> 00:37:58.999
No... You won't take a
step unless I allow you to.

348
00:37:59.600 --> 00:38:03.399
What is it? Are you
surprised. Halime?

349
00:38:04.080 --> 00:38:07.199
It's because I joined the
battle without letting you know.

350
00:38:07.240 --> 00:38:10.079
Are you going to yell at me
like my father did. mother?

351
00:38:10.160 --> 00:38:12.639
You joined that battle
without my permission.

352
00:38:12.680 --> 00:38:15.919
You entered your father's
tent without my permission!

353
00:38:16.040 --> 00:38:18.239
When are you going
to listen to me. Halime?

354
00:38:18.360 --> 00:38:19.599
What is it then?

355
00:38:19.800 --> 00:38:22.279
Should I have left my
brother alon in the war?

356
00:38:22.440 --> 00:38:23.799
You are being stubborn.

357
00:38:23.840 --> 00:38:26.919
You get in trouble and you are
dragging your sisters with you.

358
00:38:27.120 --> 00:38:29.799
Mother I am
the head of sisters!

359
00:38:29.840 --> 00:38:33.799
-I and my sisters deserve to fight
on the battlefield! -Not anymore.

360
00:38:34.400 --> 00:38:36.479
I dismissed you.

361
00:38:36.560 --> 00:38:40.039
You are not the head
of sisters anymore.

362
00:38:42.160 --> 00:38:43.679
Mother...

363
00:38:43.680 --> 00:38:45.639
What are you saying? Don't.

364
00:38:45.680 --> 00:38:49.639
From now on. you will not leave
this tribe unless I allow you to.

365
00:38:49.680 --> 00:38:52.359
Don't worry. it s not going
to be this way forever.

366
00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:57.119
It's until a Bey whom I consider appropriate
comes and takes you as his bride.

367
00:38:58.120 --> 00:39:01.399
-Mother ..
-Now sit and start preparing your dowry.

368
00:39:01.600 --> 00:39:05.079
Your hands must not hold
swords but embroider now.

369
00:39:39.960 --> 00:39:44.319
You split this great tribe in two
with one word of yours. Osman Bey.

370
00:39:44.480 --> 00:39:47.719
Your Alps. Boys.
daughters-in-law.

371
00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:54.119
What if it doesn't stop growing.

372
00:39:55.680 --> 00:39:58.759
That sword belonged
on the battlefield.

373
00:39:58.840 --> 00:40:02.879
That sword would open
the gates of Bursa for us.

374
00:40:04.840 --> 00:40:07.279
The sword...

375
00:40:07.520 --> 00:40:11.239
The sword is in its place.

376
00:40:12.160 --> 00:40:14.919
The one who deserves it...

377
00:40:15.000 --> 00:40:16.839
will come and take it.

378
00:40:17.040 --> 00:40:21.879
Osman. Osman?

379
00:40:26.640 --> 00:40:30.759
Open your eyes! Open your eyes!

380
00:40:31.480 --> 00:40:33.439
Osman!

381
00:40:33.560 --> 00:40:35.159
Did he speak?

382
00:40:35.240 --> 00:40:37.159
He will speak.

383
00:40:40.200 --> 00:40:43.719
-Are you leaving?
-Yes. I am leaving.

384
00:40:43.920 --> 00:40:46.679
I should not keep
Governor Temurtas waiting.

385
00:40:46.760 --> 00:40:49.399
Thanks to him...

386
00:40:49.440 --> 00:40:52.319
Osman will lift the
siege around Bursa.

387
00:40:52.480 --> 00:40:55.039
Do you trust that Temurtas?

388
00:40:55.080 --> 00:41:01.239
When the swords become silent in
war. interests begin to speak. Flavius.

389
00:41:01.440 --> 00:41:03.399
Governor Temurtas...

390
00:41:03.720 --> 00:41:06.159
does not want
Osman to get stronger.

391
00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:10.519
And we don't want Bursa to lose.

392
00:41:13.160 --> 00:41:17.319
Whether Temurtas convinces
Osman or not. I don't care.

393
00:41:17.640 --> 00:41:20.879
I will take the revenge of
my father and brother. Saroz.

394
00:41:21.040 --> 00:41:23.559
When the right time comes...

395
00:41:24.120 --> 00:41:28.039
you will attack
the headquarters.

396
00:41:35.240 --> 00:41:39.079
Take this. merchant The
goods you brought are good.

397
00:41:40.720 --> 00:41:44.199
Orhan destroyed the
shipment coming to Bursa

398
00:41:44.320 --> 00:41:48.399
Don't worry. merchant. There
won't be a problem. Don't worry.

399
00:41:48.600 --> 00:41:50.599
Are these your men?

400
00:41:50.760 --> 00:41:54.159
Come on. my valiants!
Burn everything you see!

401
00:41:54.280 --> 00:41:57.079
Damn it! Turks!
Defend the goods!

402
00:41:57.200 --> 00:41:59.439
Defend them!

403
00:42:01.480 --> 00:42:04.039
Defend them!

404
00:42:40.120 --> 00:42:42.359
I need him alive.
do not kill him.

405
00:42:42.400 --> 00:42:45.359
I've never left any of them
survive until now. brother!

406
00:42:45.360 --> 00:42:46.399
Balaban!

407
00:42:47.320 --> 00:42:49.719
Are you going to
let others mock me?

408
00:42:50.040 --> 00:42:53.439
It's a sin to mock with someone
who has lost his mind. brother.

409
00:42:53.480 --> 00:42:55.439
Don't worry no
one will talk about it.

410
00:42:55.480 --> 00:42:57.839
Come on. stop being stubborn.

411
00:42:57.960 --> 00:43:01.039
Alright.

412
00:43:01.800 --> 00:43:06.479
The world I just a handful of soil
for us. We will surely meet again.

413
00:43:16.080 --> 00:43:19.999
Listen to me carefully! Go and
tell th dogs that guard Bursa...

414
00:43:20.040 --> 00:43:23.679
From now on. every shipment going
to Bursa will be destroyed in a fire...

415
00:43:23.800 --> 00:43:26.719
and every soldier
will meet death.

416
00:43:27.640 --> 00:43:30.399
Go now!

417
00:43:40.360 --> 00:43:42.919
Orhan Bey's coming.

418
00:43:43.120 --> 00:43:45.759
-My Bey is here.
-Father.

419
00:43:47.080 --> 00:43:50.279
Come here. my sons.

420
00:43:54.120 --> 00:43:59.519
They say you aren't the commander
anymore Is that right father?

421
00:44:01.760 --> 00:44:03.439
You don't have your sword.

422
00:44:03.800 --> 00:44:06.719
I ouldn't stop them
my Bey. They heard.

423
00:44:07.200 --> 00:44:09.439
Dark news spreads
fast they say.

424
00:44:09.440 --> 00:44:11.319
Right. I'm not the
commander anymore.

425
00:44:11.360 --> 00:44:14.079
But I will keep fighting
for your grandfather.

426
00:44:14.280 --> 00:44:16.999
When it's time. so will you.

427
00:44:17.480 --> 00:44:20.839
Does my grandfather not love
you because you lost. father?

428
00:44:21.080 --> 00:44:23.999
-Kasim.
-Orhan Bey!

429
00:44:29.400 --> 00:44:31.999
Let's practice on
the horse. boys.

430
00:44:32.000 --> 00:44:36.319
Orhan Bey Osman Bey
ish't well. He blacked out.

431
00:44:46.560 --> 00:44:48.479

432
00:44:48.800 --> 00:44:50.799
Father.

433
00:44:51.200 --> 00:44:53.159
What happened. mother?

434
00:44:53.480 --> 00:44:55.839
He was fine before
you came to the tent.

435
00:44:55.920 --> 00:44:58.199
It seems you burned his
hearts with your words.

436
00:44:58.240 --> 00:45:00.559
Watch your words. Alaeddin.

437
00:45:00.840 --> 00:45:04.319
Enough! You are in the
presence of your father.

438
00:45:04.600 --> 00:45:07.839
Your father blacked
out. burning in fever.

439
00:45:09.600 --> 00:45:11.599
Father.

440
00:45:12.160 --> 00:45:14.479
Father.

441
00:45:14.800 --> 00:45:17.519
Father?

442
00:45:20.480 --> 00:45:22.879
Malhun.

443
00:45:25.680 --> 00:45:28.039
My sons.

444
00:45:29.240 --> 00:45:32.159
I'm fine. I'm fine.

445
00:45:34.680 --> 00:45:38.519
-Thanks to Allah.
-What happened. father?

446
00:45:39.120 --> 00:45:41.799
It's nothing. Orhan.

447
00:45:41.920 --> 00:45:44.799
I said I'm fine.

448
00:45:46.520 --> 00:45:48.679
You are fine.

449
00:45:49.160 --> 00:45:51.359
Osman.

450
00:45:57.480 --> 00:45:59.359
We are all going
through hard times.

451
00:45:59.440 --> 00:46:03.599
Yet father hasn't been eating since
he got the news about Bursa. Alaeddin.

452
00:46:04.760 --> 00:46:09.079
You can see nothing but yourself.
How did you even see the father. Gonca;

453
00:46:11.400 --> 00:46:13.199
Watch your words.

454
00:46:13.360 --> 00:46:16.199
Gonca. Nilufer. Get out.

455
00:47:15.080 --> 00:47:19.079
Are you Cerkutay the
blacksheep of Mongolians?

456
00:47:20.440 --> 00:47:25.799
I'm Cerkutay.
Osman Bey's fellow.

457
00:47:31.760 --> 00:47:34.679
Why did you come?

458
00:47:35.760 --> 00:47:40.119
I'm the mes enger of Temurtas Noyan.
the heir of the great Ilkhanid State.

459
00:47:40.240 --> 00:47:42.519
Wow. wow. wow.

460
00:47:42.840 --> 00:47:45.839
I will talk to Osman Bey.

461
00:47:58.120 --> 00:47:58.879

462
00:47:58.880 --> 00:48:01.559
Follow me.

463
00:48:40.280 --> 00:48:42.919
My Bey.

464
00:48:44.080 --> 00:48:47.999
The messenger of Ilkhanid
Governor Temurtas Noyan is here.

465
00:48:50.400 --> 00:48:53.119
He wants to see you
What should I tell him?

466
00:48:56.680 --> 00:48:59.199
-Get me up.
-Father.

467
00:48:59.480 --> 00:49:01.999
I can talk to him if
you let me. my Bey.

468
00:49:02.200 --> 00:49:04.679
We should welcome him.

469
00:49:08.160 --> 00:49:11.559
Bismillahirrahmanirrahim.

470
00:49:11.880 --> 00:49:16.279
Let's see what they want.

471
00:49:20.120 --> 00:49:23.359
My Allah. give him strength.

472
00:49:55.600 --> 00:50:00.879
