and what he promised for the governor.

473
00:50:11.640 --> 00:50:14.359
No need for counting.

474
00:50:14.880 --> 00:50:18.239
It s incomplete
again. How do I know?

475
00:50:18.520 --> 00:50:20.359
The shame on your face.

476
00:50:20.600 --> 00:50:25.759
As you know. Osman. He holds
the trade routes blocked for years.

477
00:50:25.920 --> 00:50:29.719
-Orhan doesn't let any carriages pass...
-Enough!

478
00:50:31.680 --> 00:50:38.879
Every time. on your knees. With
the same excuses and same excuses.

479
00:50:41.280 --> 00:50:44.359
We have spared
your lives so far.

480
00:50:44.880 --> 00:50:50.719
So you wouldn't complain
about Kayi but deal with them!

481
00:50:51.120 --> 00:50:52.959
And what do you do?

482
00:50:53.200 --> 00:50:56.239
What do you do?

483
00:50:58.560 --> 00:51:02.999
Karesi. Karesi...
He is being a pirat!

484
00:51:05.960 --> 00:51:09.799
You th other beys are
conflicting with each other.

485
00:51:09.880 --> 00:51:12.119
And what i1s Orhan
doing in the meantime?

486
00:51:12.440 --> 00:51:16.799
He is seeking more conquests!

487
00:51:17.480 --> 00:51:20.999
And Turkmen Beylics
hearing that he got victorious...

488
00:51:21.880 --> 00:51:23.719
run to Osman's Beylic.

489
00:51:23.840 --> 00:51:29.879
I didn t call you over to make
you pay your tax of few coins..

490
00:51:31.200 --> 00:51:34.319
But tell you to pull
yourselves together!

491
00:51:34.480 --> 00:51:38.759
Either you will stand
united against Osman...

492
00:51:38.880 --> 00:51:44.999
or you will vanish under
the feet of Ilkhanid horsemen!

493
00:52:03.040 --> 00:52:04.879
Speak. messenger.

494
00:52:05.000 --> 00:52:08.759
I've brought greetings from Temurtas
Noyan. the governor of Ilkhanid.

495
00:52:08.920 --> 00:52:10.519
Aleykum selam.

496
00:52:10.600 --> 00:52:15.679
He wants to talk about both the siege of
Bursa and the trad routes that you blocked.

497
00:52:15.800 --> 00:52:19.839
Tomorrow. he will be waiting for you in
Cavdar Tribe in the Germiyan border.

498
00:52:29.800 --> 00:52:34.399
Well... My father will
declare his decision shortly.

499
00:52:34.560 --> 00:52:37.199
You wait outside.

500
00:52:44.640 --> 00:52:46.719
Father.

501
00:52:48.160 --> 00:52:52.159
-Osman Bey.
-Father. are you alright?

502
00:52:53.800 --> 00:52:57.559
Father. you cant
go meet him hike this.

503
00:52:58.240 --> 00:53:00.559
Someone has to go.

504
00:53:00.800 --> 00:53:08.679
As the regent of
mine in the meeting.

505
00:53:13.680 --> 00:53:18.839
Alaeddin and
Sahinshah will be there.

506
00:53:28.480 --> 00:53:31.639
Bring the doctor immediately!

507
00:53:38.960 --> 00:53:43.039
Governor Temurtas if
the Ilkhanid rmy help us...

508
00:53:44.480 --> 00:53:49.359
Bursa managed on
their own. On their own!

509
00:53:49.840 --> 00:53:53.879
But all you Beylics
can't manage!

510
00:53:54.120 --> 00:53:57.519
Then you beg for an
army from Ilkhanate.

511
00:53:57.760 --> 00:54:01.999
Is that so? Is that?

512
00:54:13.080 --> 00:54:16.319
There is only one
favor I can do for you.

513
00:54:17.560 --> 00:54:20.759
Removing the siege.

514
00:54:22.560 --> 00:54:25.239
And reopening the trade routes.

515
00:54:25.400 --> 00:54:30.319
So you an also
earn money as before.

516
00:54:31.200 --> 00:54:33.759
pay your taxes.

517
00:54:34.040 --> 00:54:40.279
and reinforce army or do
whatever you want with the money left.

518
00:54:40.480 --> 00:54:42.639
Alright.

519
00:55:12.720 --> 00:55:16.919
While my poison is
flowing inside Osman's tent.

520
00:55:18.200 --> 00:55:22.079
this table where Kayi
accept whatever I say...

521
00:55:22.760 --> 00:55:25.399
will have important
guests soon.

522
00:55:25.760 --> 00:55:28.599
Very important.

523
00:55:29.880 --> 00:55:34.479
And I d cide
who will be invited.

524
00:55:36.120 --> 00:55:42.999
Sahinshah hit the road
with Alaeddin at dawn.

525
00:55:43.600 --> 00:55:45.519
As you order my Bey.

526
00:55:45.680 --> 00:55:50.119
Who will take the command in the
headquarters during my absence. my Bey?

527
00:55:57.880 --> 00:56:00.359
Cerkutay.

528
00:56:01.960 --> 00:56:05.519
It's your duty.

529
00:56:11.120 --> 00:56:15.399
-As you order. my Bey.
-Come on. what are you waiting for here?

530
00:56:15.760 --> 00:56:18.519
Everybody get to work.

531
00:56:20.480 --> 00:56:23.039
Let's go. Sahinshah Bey.

532
00:56:24.160 --> 00:56:26.799
Orhan.

533
00:56:31.320 --> 00:56:35.319
Bring Boran to me.

534
00:56:40.960 --> 00:56:43.679
As you order. my Bey.

535
00:56:45.440 --> 00:56:51.199
I want to see him
alive before me.

536
00:57:12.760 --> 00:57:15.919
My Bey will be
alright. Orhan Bey.

537
00:57:16.040 --> 00:57:18.759
He will get better
when Boran Bey is here.

538
00:57:20.240 --> 00:57:23.759
What if he gets worse when he
sees my companion s lifeless body?

539
00:57:24.000 --> 00:57:28.319
We don t even know
if he is alive or dead.

540
00:57:29.040 --> 00:57:33.679
You killed my father!
You killed my brother!

541
00:57:34.080 --> 00:57:37.319
Your father was injured!

542
00:57:37.480 --> 00:57:41.199
Osman Bey treated his
wounds with his own hands!

543
00:57:48.280 --> 00:57:52.399
That's a lie.

544
00:57:52.440 --> 00:57:54.799
Cerkutay Bey...

545
00:57:54.880 --> 00:57:59.359
I hope Boran Bey is alive. I am
sure Flavius will want to use him.

546
00:57:59.600 --> 00:58:03.519
We will bring him here alive. or
we will bring Saroz' head here.

547
00:58:05.280 --> 00:58:07.879
My Bey. what are you saying?

548
00:58:08.240 --> 00:58:11.599
My Bey...

549
00:58:12.200 --> 00:58:14.839
I... I don't...

550
00:58:15.040 --> 00:58:19.319
I don t know what to say or think. Should
I be happy about my brother's survival?

551
00:58:19.360 --> 00:58:22.799
Should I be upset
about my Bey's sickness?

552
00:58:23.680 --> 00:58:26.159
Or your dismissal...

553
00:58:26.320 --> 00:58:29.279
We will not lose our
hope. Cerkutay Bey.

554
00:58:29.320 --> 00:58:33.079
Osman Bey s test is not
just for me. but is for all of us.

555
00:58:33.080 --> 00:58:35.839
And I am sure we
will get over this.

556
00:58:36.120 --> 00:58:39.079
I just need to know
who is by my side.

557
00:58:39.640 --> 00:58:42.559
I will always be by
your side. my Bey.

558
00:58:42.560 --> 00:58:45.719
Thank you.

559
00:58:58.160 --> 00:59:00.679
The headquarters
is entrusted to you.

560
00:59:00.840 --> 00:59:02.839
Boran Bey is entrusted to me.

561
00:59:03.120 --> 00:59:06.759
Let's set out. We
will think on the way.

562
00:59:22.800 --> 00:59:26.559
Greetings to you. Ilkhanate's
precious Governor Temurtas!

563
00:59:26.680 --> 00:59:29.559
We have no tim to
lose with greetings!

564
00:59:29.640 --> 00:59:32.759
Come and sit here. Saroz.

565
00:59:45.800 --> 00:59:52.319
Doesn't someone who defended
Bursa alone for so many years..

566
00:59:52.400 --> 00:59:55.359
Deserve a better
welcome Temurtas?

567
00:59:55.400 --> 00:59:57.199
Why?

568
00:59:57.320 --> 01:00:01.519
I invited you to my table.
What else do you want. Saroz?

569
01:00:02.240 --> 01:00:02.759
Look.

570
01:00:02.760 --> 01:00:07.639
Do you see Turk Beys' envoys there? They are
standing there and watching us in a helpless state.

571
01:00:07.880 --> 01:00:14.599
Just be ause you defeated Orhan alone. do you
consider yourself equal to the Ilkhanate's governor?

572
01:00:18.040 --> 01:00:22.279
I am not here to
see their ugly faces...

573
01:00:22.400 --> 01:00:25.919
I am here to see
Osman s old face...

574
01:00:26.040 --> 01:00:29.879
wrinkled with
defeat. Governor Bey.

575
01:00:30.920 --> 01:00:34.239
Unfortunately. Unfortunately..

576
01:00:34.400 --> 01:00:39.159
Neither Orhan nor
Osman won't join us Saroz.

577
01:00:39.800 --> 01:00:43.479
Orhan fell out of
favor thanks to you.

578
01:00:43.800 --> 01:00:48.999
And Osman is in his
deathbed thanks tom.

579
01:00:49.400 --> 01:00:55.679
So who will Kayi
send to this lion's den?

580
01:00:56.200 --> 01:00:59.759
The sheep named Alaeddin?

581
01:01:00.400 --> 01:01:05.359
Thank you for all
this bother. Temurtas.

582
01:01:06.080 --> 01:01:09.359
But I..

583
01:01:09.640 --> 01:01:13.479
Am going to wait
for tasting the sheep.

584
01:01:15.240 --> 01:01:17.159
What are you saying. Orhan?

585
01:01:17.240 --> 01:01:20.519
He dismissed you first. Now
Is he sending you to death?

586
01:01:20.560 --> 01:01:23.039
That was maybe the
last request of my father.

587
01:01:23.160 --> 01:01:26.599
I will find Boran.
Dead or alive.

588
01:01:26.760 --> 01:01:30.279
All this happened just when
Temurtas came to the frontiers.

589
01:01:30.320 --> 01:01:32.239
Is there something you suspect?

590
01:01:35.080 --> 01:01:37.239
The doctor...

591
01:01:37.480 --> 01:01:41.599
He was acting different. He was wearing
gloves as he was applying the ointment.

592
01:01:41.760 --> 01:01:44.199
I've never seen that before.

593
01:01:44.240 --> 01:01:48.039
We have known him for a very long
time. He helped us for many times but..

594
01:01:48.280 --> 01:01:50.439
I know. I know but..

595
01:01:50.480 --> 01:01:53.719
I want you to watch out.

596
01:01:53.840 --> 01:01:58.199
My Bey... We are
ready. We can leave.

597
01:01:58.800 --> 01:02:04.399
Investigate this matter. The kids
and my father are entrusted to you.

598
01:02:10.760 --> 01:02:14.119
Ilkhanate will hear
the help cries of Bursa.

599
01:02:14.240 --> 01:02:17.639
The siege will be lifted. the
trade routes will be opened.

600
01:02:17.840 --> 01:02:20.719
So. when we leave this tabl ...

601
01:02:20.760 --> 01:02:24.839
what will happen to the
dark clouds over Bursa. Saroz?

602
01:02:25.000 --> 01:02:26.759
They will disappear.

603
01:02:26.880 --> 01:02:33.519
What if those dark clouds
are over the Ilkhanate..

604
01:02:33.720 --> 01:02:37.119
Temurtas.

605
01:02:41.560 --> 01:02:45.799
I don't understand.
Osman blocked your Silk Road.

606
01:02:45.920 --> 01:02:50.479
Orhan blocked the
path of their Beys.

607
01:02:51.000 --> 01:02:54.119
With the few gold
coins you ve collected.

608
01:02:54.160 --> 01:03:01.719
you can only set up such a table.
let alone an army. right Temurtas?

609
01:03:02.280 --> 01:03:08.039
What you gave me wasn't
a gift. it was out of necessity.

610
01:03:22.640 --> 01:03:27.039
I will erase the Kayi
tribe from history.

611
01:03:28.360 --> 01:03:36.279
Orhan's defeat. Osman's
illness. our alliance.

612
01:03:39.880 --> 01:03:45.719
I ok if you fail.
I will go my own way.

613
01:03:46.080 --> 01:03:52.319
I'm the only one who
has ever defeated Orhan.

614
01:03:53.960 --> 01:03:56.679
Thanks to my
commander Flavius ..

615
01:03:56.720 --> 01:04:02.759
I can destroy their headquarters
and defeat them again.

616
01:04:03.120 --> 01:04:06.799
Without needing you.

617
01:04:07.960 --> 01:04:14.119
So show me your strength.

618
01:04:23.360 --> 01:04:28.079
May you go safely. my Bey. InshaAllah
you will succeed in your new duty.

619
01:04:28.240 --> 01:04:30.759
Do you know what
my duty is. Aykurt?

620
01:04:30.800 --> 01:04:35.119
My Bey... Even if you don't have a
duty. you will be the most success...

621
01:04:35.160 --> 01:04:38.839
Duties do not determine
positions. Aykurt.

622
01:04:38.920 --> 01:04:43.039
Orhan Bey will
always be Orhan Bey.

623
01:04:43.600 --> 01:04:46.039
EyvAllah.

624
01:04:46.120 --> 01:04:48.839
Where are you going. Orhan Bey?

625
01:04:48.920 --> 01:04:51.439
I and the Alps have
been fighting for years.

626
01:04:51.440 --> 01:04:54.479
I deserve asking for their
pardon right. Alaeddin?

627
01:04:54.600 --> 01:04:56.599
Sure you do. brother.

628
01:04:56.720 --> 01:04:59.479
Our pardon is also halal to you.

629
01:04:59.520 --> 01:05:01.359
You did at the council.

630
01:05:01.760 --> 01:05:04.919
And you prayed for me. I heard.

631
01:05:05.120 --> 01:05:10.039
Your father prays. we can
just say 'Aameen". Orhan Bey.

632
01:05:10.080 --> 01:05:15.119
Don t you know my father
brother? He made his decision.

633
01:05:15.720 --> 01:05:18.239
I know you are hurt.

634
01:05:18.480 --> 01:05:22.079
But this decision...

635
01:05:22.200 --> 01:05:25.159
will never overshadow
your victories and conquests.

636
01:05:25.400 --> 01:05:30.839
Your shadow also must
not be over Bursa now.

637
01:05:31.480 --> 01:05:35.479
-I am saying that be ause I care about you.
-Don't worry Sahinshah Bey.

638
01:05:35.600 --> 01:05:40.119
From now on. Bursa will b yours.
mountains and valleys will be ours.

639
01:05:49.960 --> 01:05:52.839
We are here. my Bey!

640
01:05:59.040 --> 01:06:00.999
May you go safely. brother.

641
01:06:01.160 --> 01:06:03.279
You too brother..

642
01:06:03.400 --> 01:06:07.359
Brother.. Even if we go
in different directions...

643
01:06:07.760 --> 01:06:11.359
we will both follow the path
my father leads. InshaAllah.

644
01:06:11.680 --> 01:06:16.239
It's better than facing each
other on the same path. brother.

645
01:06:16.320 --> 01:06:18.919
May Allah be with you.

646
01:06:42.880 --> 01:06:47.199
Continue giving the medicines I
prepared earlier. Malhun Hatun.

647
01:06:47.280 --> 01:06:50.439
Won't you prepare
a new medicine?

648
01:06:50.640 --> 01:06:53.479
There is no need for now.

649
01:06:53.680 --> 01:06:56.919
What do you mean?
My father was recovering.

650
01:06:57.240 --> 01:07:00.639
Why did he suddenly
get weak like this?

651
01:07:00.920 --> 01:07:04.359
There is nothing to worry
about. It s how this illness is.

652
01:07:04.600 --> 01:07:06.319
It gets stronger and weaker.

653
01:07:06.400 --> 01:07:11.239
But you used to say different
things before. Doctor Efendi.

654
01:07:11.800 --> 01:07:14.239
Is there something
you're hesitant to tell us?

655
01:07:14.440 --> 01:07:18.879
Nilufer Hatun.. This
Illness requires a good rest.

656
01:07:19.080 --> 01:07:21.119
But our Bey never stops.

657
01:07:21.280 --> 01:07:24.319
He is tired.

658
01:07:25.800 --> 01:07:29.079
It's not just..
Nilufer. alright.

659
01:07:29.080 --> 01:07:33.519
Doctor Efendi is doing
his best. We can leave.

660
01:07:46.200 --> 01:07:49.159
Aunt...

661
01:07:49.320 --> 01:07:52.559
What happened? You
were questioning the man.

662
01:07:52.640 --> 01:07:54.279
Your brother thinks that...

663
01:07:54.400 --> 01:08:00.359
your father's iliness getting worse right when
he was about to meet Temurtas was not a coincidence.

664
01:08:04.840 --> 01:08:09.159
Did they make my father si kb cause
they didn't want him to go to that meeting?

665
01:08:09.240 --> 01:08:12.639
He was alright in the morning.
It all happened in a short time.

666
01:08:12.720 --> 01:08:15.559
Now Alaeddin and Sahinshah
will go to that meeting.

667
01:08:15.560 --> 01:08:19.719
The only person who can get
close to my father is the doctor.

668
01:08:19.840 --> 01:08:21.679
We will follow him.

669
01:08:23.560 --> 01:08:26.679
InshaAllah Orhan is not right.

670
01:08:27.320 --> 01:08:29.599
We'll start firing soon.

671
01:08:29.640 --> 01:08:32.999
Have the catapults repaired.

672
01:08:41.600 --> 01:08:43.239
What are they doing here?

673
01:08:43.280 --> 01:08:47.039
We will see now.

674
01:08:51.240 --> 01:08:53.319
Selamun al ykum.

675
01:08:53.480 --> 01:08:55.959
Aleykum selam.

676
01:09:08.840 --> 01:09:13.159
May it be good Orhan Bey.
Didn't our Bey dismiss you?

677
01:09:13.480 --> 01:09:19.319
What are you doing here? Where
is our Commander Sahinshah Bey?

678
01:09:20.760 --> 01:09:24.359
Your Commander Sahinshah Bey...

679
01:09:24.520 --> 01:09:27.359
with the duty given
by my Osman Bey..

680
01:09:27.480 --> 01:09:35.239
Went to Cavdar tribe And he
gave me this duty to represent him.

681
01:09:35.560 --> 01:09:43.079
And my Orhan Bey is here to say goodbye
to the Alps and ask for their pardon.

682
01:09:49.360 --> 01:09:51.439
All our rights are
halal to you. my Bey.

683
01:09:51.520 --> 01:09:55.159
May it be halal. my Bey.

684
01:09:55.920 --> 01:10:00.079
And since he is her already...

685
01:10:00.520 --> 01:10:06.119
he will be my guest in
my tent until his Alps return.

686
01:10:08.600 --> 01:10:12.119
Orhan Bey. Come. my Bey.

687
01:10:22.320 --> 01:10:26.759
How could he come
all the way to her?

688
01:10:26.960 --> 01:10:30.679
His Alps are here as well.

689
01:10:33.400 --> 01:10:35.159
He will leave soon.

690
01:10:35.200 --> 01:10:39.159
If he tries to stay. we
will show him the way.

691
01:10:39.280 --> 01:10:41.519
My Bey is in the tent.

692
01:10:46.840 --> 01:10:48.799
He is in the tent..

693
01:10:48.800 --> 01:10:52.799
But the tent does not
belong to him anymore.

694
01:11:05.120 --> 01:11:08.159
My Bey. What is happening?
We don't understand anything!

695
01:11:08.320 --> 01:11:12.319
Our Orhan Bey has a more
important duty now. Balaban.

696
01:11:15.040 --> 01:11:17.199
Now listen to me carefully..

697
01:11:17.440 --> 01:11:21.999
We will get in Bursa.
take Boran Bey and leave.

698
01:11:24.920 --> 01:11:26.159
Cerkutay Bey will..

699
01:11:26.240 --> 01:11:30.959
Go to the city walls at night and offer
Saroz ten captives in exchange for Boran Bey.

700
01:11:30.960 --> 01:11:32.559
They won't give him
back to us. my Bey.

701
01:11:32.560 --> 01:11:34.679
Boran Bey is the man
closest to Osman Bey.

702
01:11:34.680 --> 01:11:37.839
They will want to cut him into
pieces and learn what he knows.

703
01:11:37.840 --> 01:11:39.879
That's what I told Orhan Bey.

704
01:11:39.960 --> 01:11:41.399
And he said it was right.

705
01:11:41.440 --> 01:11:44.399
He said I was going to insist and
they wouldn t give him back to us.

706
01:11:44.400 --> 01:11:46.039
The bargaining would
become Intense...

707
01:11:46.040 --> 01:11:47.999
and when the
attention is on me...

708
01:11:48.040 --> 01:11:51.319
At that moment. the four
of us will sneak in the castle.

709
01:11:51.520 --> 01:11:53.919
We can do that. my Bey. How?

710
01:11:54.000 --> 01:11:56.519
We will enter Bursa
Castle from the cliff side.

711
01:11:56.640 --> 01:12:00.319
They will be unwary because they
believe there will be no attack from there.

712
01:12:00.360 --> 01:12:02.919
When Orhan Bey sent
Boran Bey he sent me along...

713
01:12:02.920 --> 01:12:06.279
so I could see
where he entered.

714
01:12:11.760 --> 01:12:14.959
My Bey. should you
reconsider it? I am still worried.

715
01:12:15.120 --> 01:12:18.999
What if what happened to
Boran happens to you too?

716
01:12:19.080 --> 01:12:25.519
I put Boran Bey in that difficult situation Either
I will save him from there. or I will die in there.

717
01:12:38.720 --> 01:12:41.719
are weighed down
by the siege. Hatun.

718
01:12:41.920 --> 01:12:44.959
And th state of the
treasury is not good.

719
01:12:45.360 --> 01:12:49.039
We have no other choice
than conquering Bursa quickly.

720
01:12:49.080 --> 01:12:51.239
Here.

721
01:12:51.360 --> 01:12:56.359
Thank you Hatun. Health to your
hands. BismillahirRahmaniRahim.

722
01:12:56.560 --> 01:12:59.039
You are right. Alaeddin.

723
01:12:59.080 --> 01:13:01.599
But... Now Sahinshah Bey...

724
01:13:01.720 --> 01:13:05.359
Is it your
disposal. Alaeddin.

725
01:13:05.720 --> 01:13:08.479
What are you
trying to say. Hatun?

726
01:13:08.640 --> 01:13:12.639
I am trying to say that
he will be protecting you.

727
01:13:12.960 --> 01:13:16.039
If Orhan was here. you wouldn't
know what would happen.

728
01:13:16.400 --> 01:13:19.759
As my father's iIllness
got worse each day...

729
01:13:19.920 --> 01:13:23.279
may Allah bless him.
he gave you your duties.

730
01:13:23.360 --> 01:13:25.879
Besides...

731
01:13:25.960 --> 01:13:28.319
my father saw
the strength in you.

732
01:13:28.480 --> 01:13:30.599
He ntrusted the Beylic to you.

733
01:13:30.760 --> 01:13:33.159
You and Sahinshah Bey...

734
01:13:33.320 --> 01:13:37.519
will strengthen our Beylic and
take Bursa with Allah's permission.

735
01:13:42.320 --> 01:13:44.919
Watch out for Malhun
Hatun and Halime. alright?

736
01:13:44.920 --> 01:13:50.559
If only you could see how angry she was
when she first heard the news. Alaeddin...

737
01:13:51.240 --> 01:13:53.559
I wonder what she
said at the council..

738
01:13:54.960 --> 01:13:56.239
Right...

739
01:13:58.080 --> 01:14:01.879
She is acting like I am a man who
would steal something from his brother.

740
01:14:02.120 --> 01:14:04.839
Towba astaghfirullah.

741
01:14:05.120 --> 01:14:08.039
Allah is my witness. Hatun...

742
01:14:08.200 --> 01:14:12.159
I just want the
well-being of our state.

743
01:14:12.960 --> 01:14:15.199
I know.

744
01:14:15.920 --> 01:14:19.199
I know you are not worried about
anything else. my Alaeddin Ali.

745
01:14:19.960 --> 01:14:23.399
But apparently. Malhun Hatun
will take Orhan Bey's side.

746
01:14:23.480 --> 01:14:25.599
And we will be left alone.

747
01:14:26.040 --> 01:14:29.959
No. Don't worry Hatun.

748
01:14:30.200 --> 01:14:33.759
I have the Beys behind me.

749
01:14:38.080 --> 01:14:41.279
Come on! Sir they are here.

750
01:14:56.280 --> 01:14:59.839
Well. well. well...

751
01:15:01.120 --> 01:15:03.479
Selamun aleykum.

752
01:15:03.600 --> 01:15:06.719
Why are you here?
To die in Bursa. again?

753
01:15:07.280 --> 01:15:11.359
To talk and to
make an agreement.

754
01:15:12.520 --> 01:15:14.719
Give Boran to me...

755
01:15:14.760 --> 01:15:19.759
and I will give you your
ten soldiers back in return.

756
01:15:20.360 --> 01:15:24.519
I will give Boran back
to you after he speaks.

757
01:15:24.840 --> 01:15:28.479
I mean. his dead body.

758
01:15:50.320 --> 01:15:52.559
This is the place. my Bey.

759
01:15:58.200 --> 01:16:01.159
Keeping Boran
will not help you...

760
01:16:01.400 --> 01:16:03.399
you cannot make him speak.

761
01:16:03.440 --> 01:16:06.039
And he won't speak anyway.

762
01:16:06.360 --> 01:16:09.159
You might be right.

763
01:16:09.240 --> 01:16:12.199
But I can make you suffer
by keeping Boran here.

764
01:16:12.400 --> 01:16:14.159
Right?

765
01:16:14.360 --> 01:16:16.439
What does Osman
Bey say about this?

766
01:16:16.640 --> 01:16:20.679
Cut it short. Will you
give Boran back to us...

767
01:16:20.880 --> 01:16:22.439
or not.

768
01:16:30.160 --> 01:16:32.999
-Let us go and save Boran.
-Come on.

769
01:16:33.800 --> 01:16:36.959
Bismillah.

770
01:16:46.440 --> 01:16:49.599
You killed my brother.

771
01:16:50.080 --> 01:16:52.679
I will have my
revenge sooner or later.

772
01:16:55.240 --> 01:16:57.239
However!

773
01:16:57.280 --> 01:17:00.199
My soldiers are valuable to me.

774
01:17:00.520 --> 01:17:03.559
How ever ten
soldi rs for Boran..

775
01:17:03.680 --> 01:17:07.079
-is a little too few.
-What?

776
01:17:07.400 --> 01:17:10.239
-What do you want?
-Twenty.

777
01:17:10.440 --> 01:17:12.639
Twenty?!

778
01:17:12.640 --> 01:17:15.839
Twenty of my soldiers for Boran.

779
01:17:16.760 --> 01:17:19.239
Twenty.

780
01:17:40.560 --> 01:17:42.999
My patience has
its limits. Cerkutay!

781
01:17:43.080 --> 01:17:45.999
Say what you will.

782
01:17:49.520 --> 01:17:54.239
My Bey. I hope you
are insid already.

783
01:18:16.400 --> 01:18:19.719
Alright! You have a deal.

784
01:18:20.320 --> 01:18:22.839
Prepare Boran.

785
01:18:23.160 --> 01:18:27.999
I will ome back with twenty
of your soldiers tomorrow.

786
01:18:30.440 --> 01:18:34.119
InshaAllah Orhan Bey made it.

787
01:18:34.320 --> 01:18:36.719
Come on.

788
01:18:44.080 --> 01:18:47.959
Sir. Boran is an important captive.
We had things to learn from him.

789
01:18:48.080 --> 01:18:51.159
Who said I will give him up?

790
01:19:08.840 --> 01:19:12.799
Bursa. Dream of my father.

791
01:19:13.360 --> 01:19:15.239
Future of my people.

792
01:19:16.160 --> 01:19:18.559
It is my destiny.

793
01:19:18.800 --> 01:19:21.439
I will have you one day.

794
01:19:22.080 --> 01:19:25.079
Not with climbing your walls.

795
01:19:25.360 --> 01:19:29.919
The day I will walk
through your doors is near.

796
01:20:25.800 --> 01:20:30.039
-My Bey you are right they are after something.
-We will find out.

797
01:20:30.440 --> 01:20:33.399
Let us save Boran Bey first.

798
01:20:40.040 --> 01:20:41.919
His fever does not go out.

799
01:20:42.080 --> 01:20:45.959
My father will be alright
with our prayers. inshaAllah.

800
01:20:47.160 --> 01:20:51.359
Tell me. healer. Did he
get worse in my abscense?

801
01:20:51.520 --> 01:20:54.599
My Bey. it got a little
worse from time to time.

802
01:20:54.680 --> 01:20:59.279
I gave him gypsophila and
urtica as you ve commanded.

803
01:20:59.480 --> 01:21:02.239
I also gave him the
ointment you gave.

804
01:21:02.520 --> 01:21:07.959
That fall flower you put in the
ointment. put three grams more.

805
01:21:08.080 --> 01:21:11.599
I will take care of my father
myself when I come back.

806
01:21:11.800 --> 01:21:14.839
As you command my Bey.

807
01:21:17.240 --> 01:21:20.279
BismillahirRahmanirRahim.

808
01:21:21.760 --> 01:21:24.599
I do not wish to
leave my father.

809
01:21:24.680 --> 01:21:26.639
I am with him.

810
01:21:26.640 --> 01:21:30.199
You lead the Beylik
with your brother.

811
01:21:30.840 --> 01:21:35.279
That will satisfy
your father the most.

812
01:21:36.200 --> 01:21:38.719
Change the vinegar
water often. mother.

813
01:21:38.760 --> 01:21:40.439
Do not worry.

814
01:21:40.520 --> 01:21:45.279
Also. be careful of that
Temurtas and his tricks.

815
01:21:45.400 --> 01:21:48.079
Do not worry. mother.

816
01:22:03.960 --> 01:22:06.399
Strength to your
elbow Sahinsah Bey.

817
01:22:09.400 --> 01:22:13.359
BismillahirRahmanirRahim.

818
01:22:14.160 --> 01:22:18.519
Does Orhan Bey say
anything about this matter?

819
01:22:19.720 --> 01:22:23.959
He congratulates and
wishes ongoing success.

820
01:22:27.160 --> 01:22:31.519
Is his saying and ideas
are the same. you think?

821
01:22:31.800 --> 01:22:35.159
It does not matter at
this point Sahinsah Bey.

822
01:22:35.760 --> 01:22:38.759
My father gave th order.

823
01:22:39.080 --> 01:22:42.199
The duty is ours.

824
01:22:42.400 --> 01:22:45.959
As long as we support each
other. we will overcome this duty.

825
01:22:46.240 --> 01:22:48.479
EvelAllah.

826
01:22:48.600 --> 01:22:53.079
As long as your
brother stays peaceful.

827
01:22:58.000 --> 01:23:02.599
My brother is brave and
valiant. Sahinsah Bey.

828
01:23:02.640 --> 01:23:05.599
He does not put
obstacles on Beylik's way.

829
01:23:05.720 --> 01:23:09.039
He only harms himself.

830
01:23:09.160 --> 01:23:11.959
And that is my concern.

831
01:23:12.080 --> 01:23:14.799
May Allah grants everyone..

832
01:23:14.920 --> 01:23:18.319
A brother like you and a
leader like you to every Beylik.

833
01:23:18.800 --> 01:23:20.639
EyvAllah. Sahinsah Bey.

834
01:23:21.000 --> 01:23:25.599
However. this is no time
to boast but to start working.

835
01:23:26.120 --> 01:23:29.519
My brother may not have
succeeded. however..

836
01:23:29.600 --> 01:23:33.039
My father's dream
will be real. inshaAllah.

837
01:23:33.760 --> 01:23:37.399
InshaAllah.

838
01:23:37.640 --> 01:23:40.719
Come on then.

839
01:23:44.600 --> 01:23:47.919
And where is Orhan Bey?

840
01:23:49.280 --> 01:23:51.559
He went to say goodbye.

841
01:23:51.800 --> 01:23:54.439
And still haven't come back.

842
01:24:25.120 --> 01:24:27.599
-Put on your disguise.
-My Bey.

843
01:24:27.680 --> 01:24:29.519
What if soldiers recognize you?

844
01:24:29.600 --> 01:24:33.399
Allow me to enter the
dungeon in your stead.

845
01:24:33.640 --> 01:24:37.479
Your mind is needed
outside come on now.

846
01:24:44.680 --> 01:24:47.439
I do not wish to
call evil. however..

847
01:24:47.920 --> 01:24:52.959
What if Osman Bey dies?

848
01:24:53.360 --> 01:24:56.359
My Allah prevent. Hatun.

849
01:24:56.440 --> 01:24:59.479
However. preventing
this clash is a must.

850
01:24:59.600 --> 01:25:01.759
Otherwise. slanders will go on.

851
01:25:01.920 --> 01:25:04.519
Alaeddin is leading now.

852
01:25:04.760 --> 01:25:07.319
The throne is his
right after Osman Bey.

853
01:25:07.400 --> 01:25:10.639
And when he has you at his back.

854
01:25:10.720 --> 01:25:13.639
EvelAllah he can
handle the burden.

855
01:25:13.760 --> 01:25:16.959
Alaeddin is obedient.
He will histen to words.

856
01:25:17.000 --> 01:25:18.919
When he sits on
the throne tomorrow.

857
01:25:18.960 --> 01:25:21.679
He will count my
orders as his. However..

858
01:25:21.840 --> 01:25:24.239
The fact that he does
not have a successor.

859
01:25:24.320 --> 01:25:26.519
Prevents him.

860
01:25:26.640 --> 01:25:28.359
And opens Orhan's way.

861
01:25:28.520 --> 01:25:31.759
You go and convince Gonca Hatun.

862
01:25:31.880 --> 01:25:34.799
The situation is different now.

863
01:25:35.000 --> 01:25:37.399
There is no time to wait.

864
01:25:37.560 --> 01:25:40.279
Find a hatun that will
give Alaeddin sons.

865
01:25:40.280 --> 01:25:42.599
Gonca is smart.

866
01:25:42.640 --> 01:25:45.999
She will think of
his bey's future first.

867
01:25:46.240 --> 01:25:48.279
I will make that happen.

868
01:25:48.480 --> 01:25:50.959
And hurry about
Fatma situation also.

869
01:25:51.120 --> 01:25:53.439
We will ensure our
moves from all sides.

870
01:25:53.600 --> 01:25:55.839
Let Gonca be convinced first.

871
01:25:55.920 --> 01:25:58.039
Fatma will follow.

872
01:25:58.160 --> 01:25:59.839
And the rest will be up to me.

873
01:26:00.080 --> 01:26:03.199
Malhun Hatun will
want Osman Bey..

874
01:26:03.280 --> 01:26:05.319
to see her daughter's child.

875
01:26:05.560 --> 01:26:08.639
I trust you.

876
01:26:10.760 --> 01:26:14.079
Come on then. take care.

877
01:26:24.520 --> 01:26:26.879
Favius' new idea of fun
They are dumb.

878
01:26:27.000 --> 01:26:29.959
They think they can
sneak in a city like Bursa.

879
01:26:30.040 --> 01:26:32.239
We have brave
soldiers like you and me.

880
01:26:32.320 --> 01:26:34.479
Nothing will escape from us.

881
01:26:34.520 --> 01:26:36.279
Who knows what
will Flavius do now.

882
01:26:36.360 --> 01:26:38.639
Take that one to the prison
and let us go on with our duties.

883
01:26:38.720 --> 01:26:41.959
-No on informed us.
-Flavius is after a great duty.

884
01:26:42.040 --> 01:26:43.319
Our word is his.

885
01:26:43.520 --> 01:26:48.239
You an go and ask
himself if you wish.

886
01:26:51.680 --> 01:26:54.639
No need. Alright.
we will take him.

887
01:26:54.760 --> 01:26:57.839
Move. quick!

888
01:27:41.840 --> 01:27:44.559
Orhan.

889
01:27:57.640 --> 01:27:59.999
Look here son.

890
01:28:00.720 --> 01:28:03.679
My Hatun hasn't missed me a bit.

891
01:28:06.720 --> 01:28:09.319
None at all?

892
01:28:09.640 --> 01:28:12.079
If Orhan Bey Is so curious..

893
01:28:12.320 --> 01:28:14.999
He should tell first.

894
01:28:15.280 --> 01:28:18.639
Did he miss me?

895
01:28:23.640 --> 01:28:25.959
Then I won't say.

896
01:28:28.120 --> 01:28:31.279
I missed you a lot.

897
01:28:34.160 --> 01:28:36.319
However make this easy for me.

898
01:28:37.080 --> 01:28:41.399
Look here. So you are
getting fed up. Orhan Bey?

899
01:28:42.880 --> 01:28:45.719
However. I never get fed up.

900
01:28:45.800 --> 01:28:49.239
From waiting for
you. missing you.

901
01:28:53.120 --> 01:28:56.839
I never get tired
of loving you also.

902
01:28:57.200 --> 01:28:59.719
My dear.

903
01:29:04.160 --> 01:29:07.239
You will leave again.

904
01:29:07.960 --> 01:29:10.319
How will I wait for you?

905
01:29:10.360 --> 01:29:12.719
Even when we're
not together here.

906
01:29:12.840 --> 01:29:16.919
I am always with you
and you are always with me.

907
01:29:25.440 --> 01:29:28.319
And this is the proof.

908
01:29:31.640 --> 01:29:36.079
The remnants of my heart.

909
01:29:50.920 --> 01:29:53.719
Come back again alright?

910
01:29:54.040 --> 01:29:56.399
Always come back to me.

911
01:30:01.520 --> 01:30:04.439
I love you.

912
01:30:16.040 --> 01:30:18.799
I love you more.

913
01:30:27.440 --> 01:30:30.399
My Allah.

914
01:30:30.800 --> 01:30:33.599
Protect my Orhan.

915
01:30:50.600 --> 01:30:54.519
So this was a trick.

916
01:30:56.000 --> 01:30:59.599
Orhan is at Bursa. He came
in the same way Boran did.

917
01:31:00.040 --> 01:31:02.999
Find Orhan!

918
01:31:24.600 --> 01:31:26.799
Leave fast..

919
01:31:27.000 --> 01:31:30.279
And come back quickly son.

920
01:31:52.360 --> 01:31:54.759
My Osman.

921
01:31:55.080 --> 01:31:57.639
My valiant Osman.

922
01:31:57.640 --> 01:32:00.919
Are you tired?

923
01:32:01.120 --> 01:32:03.879
Or could I not..

924
01:32:04.680 --> 01:32:08.399
Help you with your burden?

925
01:32:09.960 --> 01:32:14.759
Ar you leaving me..

926
01:32:15.640 --> 01:32:18.639
Like this?

927
01:32:20.080 --> 01:32:23.599
This tribe breathes through you.

928
01:32:23.800 --> 01:32:25.999
If you leave..

929
01:32:27.200 --> 01:32:29.319
Who will breathe..

930
01:32:29.560 --> 01:32:33.759
And who will
resist in these lands?

931
01:32:43.880 --> 01:32:48.759
Your sons. of course.

932
01:32:49.320 --> 01:32:52.559
One is fire the other is water.

933
01:32:55.160 --> 01:32:57.239
They are of your heart..

934
01:32:57.360 --> 01:32:59.439
Of your heart..

935
01:32:59.560 --> 01:33:04.279
Both of them are more
ambitious more persistent than you.

936
01:33:05.920 --> 01:33:08.679
However. fire and water.

937
01:33:09.080 --> 01:33:13.159
Can not stay together.

938
01:33:13.240 --> 01:33:16.719
What if you sons clash..

939
01:33:16.760 --> 01:33:20.159
After you depart?

940
01:33:29.200 --> 01:33:30.279
No.

941
01:33:32.000 --> 01:33:34.319
No. they will not.

942
01:33:34.400 --> 01:33:37.119
They grew up with your dreams.

943
01:33:37.520 --> 01:33:42.039
Now. their only aimis to
make that dream a reality.

944
01:33:42.240 --> 01:33:45.399
Do not worry. my Bey.

945
01:33:46.000 --> 01:33:48.839
I will not have them separated.

946
01:33:50.920 --> 01:33:53.279
I will not allow it.

947
01:33:53.480 --> 01:33:54.679
Never.

948
01:34:04.120 --> 01:34:05.079
Turk!

949
01:34:06.880 --> 01:34:07.719
Turk!

950
01:34:08.960 --> 01:34:12.439
Do not die until you speak.

951
01:34:14.520 --> 01:34:17.639
Turk!
Turk!

952
01:34:17.880 --> 01:34:21.439
Is he dead?
Open the door!

953
01:34:28.680 --> 01:34:29.239
Turk.

954
01:34:57.960 --> 01:35:01.479
Boran. I'm here.

955
01:35:08.400 --> 01:35:11.999
Boran. I'm here.

956
01:35:15.920 --> 01:35:18.799
The keys are with Flavius.

957
01:35:24.360 --> 01:35:28.039
We'll see to it. don't worry.

958
01:35:29.880 --> 01:35:33.479
They will ambush the encampment.

959
01:35:33.680 --> 01:35:36.159
So that's what h
was preparing for.

960
01:36:02.760 --> 01:36:05.679
Orhan! Go!

961
01:36:06.480 --> 01:36:10.479
-Leave me here. go save yourself!
-I will not leave without you.

962
01:36:10.520 --> 01:36:13.479
I will be back Boran Bey.

963
01:36:25.200 --> 01:36:28.199
Octavius is my brother. Orhan.

964
01:36:29.080 --> 01:36:31.239
His death was your
biggest mistake.

965
01:36:31.360 --> 01:36:33.719
Your turn will come too.

966
01:36:33.880 --> 01:36:35.879
We'll see.

967
01:36:35.920 --> 01:36:39.279
Attack!

968
01:37:02.080 --> 01:37:04.999
My valiant!

969
01:37:54.400 --> 01:37:57.399
Find them!

970
01:38:09.640 --> 01:38:12.959
The city is al rted.
They're everywhere.

971
01:38:13.360 --> 01:38:14.879
Cerkutay Bey.

972
01:38:14.960 --> 01:38:18.879
They will attack the
encampment during the deal.

973
01:38:19.080 --> 01:38:21.479
What is my Bey writing?

974
01:38:25.400 --> 01:38:28.759
-Here. send it.
-Yes. my Bey.

975
01:38:32.120 --> 01:38:33.239
Bismillah.

976
01:38:36.960 --> 01:38:39.039
They are her!

977
01:38:39.120 --> 01:38:41.359
-Come on.
-They're running!

978
01:38:41.680 --> 01:38:45.119
They're heading to the walls!

979
01:38:50.040 --> 01:38:52.319
Hands off.

980
01:39:12.280 --> 01:39:16.519
What a pleasant
coincidence. Tekfur Saroz!

981
01:39:17.080 --> 01:39:22.159
So you realised Bursa will fall
upon you and took shelter here?

982
01:39:22.360 --> 01:39:26.479
